  "description": "A panoramic aerial view captures a sprawling urban landscape meeting the waters of a large bay. The foreground features a lush green hillside covered in dense trees, gradually transitioning into a tightly packed cityscape dominated by low to mid-rise buildings. Beyond the city, a wide bay stretches towards the horizon, punctuated by a bridge and distant hills. The sky is a pale blue with wispy clouds, suggesting a clear day. The composition emphasizes the scale of the urban area in relation to the natural environment.",
